<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>网络协议 - 分类 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/categories/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/</link><description>网络协议 - 分类 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/categories/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>DNS解析与CDN</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/dns%E4%B8%8Ecdn/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/dns%E4%B8%8Ecdn/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="dns解析与cdn">DNS解析与CDN</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：DNS通过分布式层级系统将域名解析为IP地址，CDN利用DNS的智能调度和边缘节点缓存，将内容分发到离用户最近的节点，二者结合是互联网性能优化的基础设施。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="dns通过分布式层级数据库实现域名到ip的映射cdn在此基础上叠加边缘缓存和智能调度">DNS通过分布式层级数据库实现域名到IP的映射，CDN在此基础上叠加边缘缓存和智能调度</h2>
<h3 id="dns域名空间树状层级结构">DNS域名空间：树状层级结构</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">                    根域名服务器 (.)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ┌────────────────────┼────────────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │                    │                    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   com                  org                  cn
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │                    │                    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> example              wikipedia            baidu
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │                    │                    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   www                 www                  www
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  记录: A 93.184.216.34
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        CNAME example.cdn.com</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>层级</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>示例</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>根域名（Root）</td>
          <td>最顶层，全球13组（字母A-M）</td>
          <td><code>.</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>顶级域（TLD）</td>
          <td>通用（gTLD）或国家/地区（ccTLD）</td>
          <td><code>.com</code> <code>.org</code> <code>.cn</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>二级域</td>
          <td>注册购买的主体域名</td>
          <td><code>example.com</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>子域</td>
          <td>二级域下的扩展</td>
          <td><code>www.example.com</code> <code>api.example.com</code></td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="dns解析流程从递归查询到本地缓存">DNS解析流程：从递归查询到本地缓存</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">用户输入 www.example.com
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 浏览器缓存 → 检查是否最近解析过
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 操作系统缓存 (/etc/hosts, DNS Client Service)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 本地DNS服务器（ISP或公共DNS如8.8.8.8）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   └── 递归查询开始 ──────────────────────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                              │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 本地DNS → 根域名服务器（.）                 │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ← 返回 com 的NS记录                        │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                              │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">5. 本地DNS → com 顶级域服务器                  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ← 返回 example.com 的NS记录                │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                              │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">6. 本地DNS → example.com 权威DNS服务器         │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   ← 返回 www.example.com 的A记录: 93.184.216.34│
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                              │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">7. 本地DNS缓存结果，返回给用户 ────────────────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">总耗时：通常 20-120ms（取决于缓存命中率）</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>DNS记录类型</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>HTTPS与TLS</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/https%E4%B8%8Etls/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/https%E4%B8%8Etls/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="https与tls">HTTPS与TLS</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：HTTPS通过TLS协议在HTTP之上提供加密、认证和完整性保护，TLS握手协商对称密钥，证书链验证服务端身份，是当前Web安全的基石。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="https通过tls协议实现加密传输身份认证和数据完整性tls握手是性能和安全的关键">HTTPS通过TLS协议实现加密传输、身份认证和数据完整性，TLS握手是性能和安全的关键</h2>
<h3 id="tlsssl演进从ssl到tls-13">TLS/SSL演进：从SSL到TLS 1.3</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>版本</th>
          <th>年份</th>
          <th>关键变化</th>
          <th>现状</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>SSL 2.0</td>
          <td>1995</td>
          <td>首个公开发布版本</td>
          <td>已废弃（严重安全漏洞）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>SSL 3.0</td>
          <td>1996</td>
          <td>广泛应用</td>
          <td>已废弃（POODLE攻击）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>TLS 1.0</td>
          <td>1999</td>
          <td>标准化，与SSL 3.0几乎相同</td>
          <td>已废弃</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>TLS 1.1</td>
          <td>2006</td>
          <td>引入显式IV防CBC攻击</td>
          <td>已废弃</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>TLS 1.2</td>
          <td>2008</td>
          <td>支持AEAD、SHA-256、扩展</td>
          <td>当前主流</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>TLS 1.3</td>
          <td>2018</td>
          <td>简化握手、删除弱算法、0-RTT</td>
          <td>推荐部署</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="tls-12-握手2-rtt建立安全连接">TLS 1.2 握手：2-RTT建立安全连接</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">客户端                                               服务端
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |        ClientHello (支持的加密套件、随机数)        |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ──────────────────────────────────────────────&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |                                                   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ServerHello (选定加密套件、随机数)                 |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  Certificate (服务端证书链)                         |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  [ServerKeyExchange] (DHE/ECDHE参数)              |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ServerHelloDone                                   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;──────────────────────────────────────────────  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |                                                   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ClientKeyExchange (预主密钥，用公钥加密)            |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  [ChangeCipherSpec]                                |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  Finished (验证握手完整性)                          |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ──────────────────────────────────────────────&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |                                                   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  [ChangeCipherSpec]                                |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  Finished                                          |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;──────────────────────────────────────────────  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |                                                   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓                                                   ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">应用数据传输（对称加密）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">总耗时：2-RTT（ClientHello → ServerHello → Finished）</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="tls-13-握手1-rtt首次-0-rtt重连">TLS 1.3 握手：1-RTT（首次）/ 0-RTT（重连）</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">首次连接（1-RTT）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">客户端                                               服务端
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ClientHello (密钥共享 + 支持的组)                 |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ──────────────────────────────────────────────&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |                                                   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ServerHello (选定密钥共享)                         |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  {EncryptedExtensions} (加密传输)                  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  {Certificate}                                     |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  {CertificateVerify}                               |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  {Finished}                                        |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;──────────────────────────────────────────────  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |                                                   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  {Finished}                                        |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ──────────────────────────────────────────────&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |                                                   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓                                                   ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">应用数据传输
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">重连（0-RTT）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  客户端发送早期数据（Early Data），使用上一次会话的PSK
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  → 无需等待服务端响应即可发送应用数据</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>TLS 1.3 的简化</strong>：</p>]]></description></item><item><title>HTTP演进</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/http%E6%BC%94%E8%BF%9B/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/http%E6%BC%94%E8%BF%9B/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="http演进">HTTP演进</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：HTTP从1.0到3.0的演进主线是&quot;减少连接数→复用连接→消除队头阻塞→降低握手延迟&quot;，每次升级都在解决前一代的瓶颈，但协议复杂度也相应增加。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="http从10到30围绕连接效率队头阻塞握手延迟三个核心问题逐步优化">HTTP从1.0到3.0围绕连接效率、队头阻塞、握手延迟三个核心问题逐步优化</h2>
<h3 id="http10无状态的请求-响应协议">HTTP/1.0：无状态的请求-响应协议</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">每次请求新建TCP连接：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">客户端                  服务端
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  TCP握手 (SYN-SYN/ACK-ACK)  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  | &lt;-------------------------&gt; |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |      GET /page1.html        |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  ------------------------&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |      200 OK + 数据           |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;------------------------  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |      TCP挥手 (FIN-ACK...)   |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  | &lt;-------------------------&gt; |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  [下一个请求重复以上全过程]</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>核心问题</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>每个请求独立TCP连接，三次握手开销大</li>
<li>无法复用连接，浏览器同时只能发少量请求（6-8个域名并发）</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="http11持久连接与管道化">HTTP/1.1：持久连接与管道化</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>特性</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>解决的问题</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>持久连接（Keep-Alive）</td>
          <td>复用TCP连接发送多个请求</td>
          <td>减少握手开销</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>管道化（Pipelining）</td>
          <td>连续发送多个请求不等待响应</td>
          <td>提高吞吐量</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>分块传输（Chunked）</td>
          <td>服务端分块发送，无需预知Content-Length</td>
          <td>动态内容传输</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>缓存控制</td>
          <td><code>Cache-Control</code>、<code>ETag</code>、<code>Last-Modified</code></td>
          <td>减少重复传输</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Host头</td>
          <td>支持同一IP多域名</td>
          <td>虚拟主机</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">HTTP/1.1 持久连接：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">客户端                  服务端
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  TCP握手                |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  | &lt;---------------------&gt; |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  GET /page1.html        |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  --------------------&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  200 OK                 |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;--------------------  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  GET /style.css         |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  --------------------&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  200 OK                 |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;--------------------  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  GET /image.jpg         |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  --------------------&gt;  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  200 OK                 |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  &lt;--------------------  |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  Connection: close      |
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  |  [可选挥手或保持]         |</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
